Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.19,0:22:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's cover Tsumego today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\1c&HFFFFFF&\fad(0,0)\3c&H09B20E&\4c&H09B20E&\bord2\shad1\pos(20,150)}T\Ns\Nu\Nm\Ne\Ng\No
